title: Listen to this if you have Imposter Syndrome
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
description:
Whether this is the first time you are hearing about Imposter Syndrome or if you have known about it for a while; I encourage you to hear me out. I speak on how I have lived with Imposter Syndrome after finding out about it from my therapist 2 years ago.. I truly hope this helps
